title: Jinan pioneers Chinese CBDC use in transportation with digital yuan bus payments
description: Jinan, the capital of Shandong Province in eastern China, has taken a proactive stance in promoting the use of China's central bank digital currency (CBDC) by initiating digital yuan payments on all of its bus routes.
